The '''XV9 turbolaser''' was a shipboard emplacement weapon produced by [[Taim & Bak/Legends|Taim & Bak]]. This heavy-duty [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolaser]] was commonly found aboard a variety of [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]].

